name: Alessia Romano
summary: Alessia Romano is a hardworking and respectful 30-year-old product manager in the technology industry. She is from Toronto but currently lives in Los Angeles, California. Alessia is multilingual, speaking English, Italian, and Spanish. Having graduated from Oracle University, she is looking for a life partner who matches her monogamous type of relationship. Alessia identifies as a straight woman, using the pronouns She/Her/Hers. She is of Hispanic or Latino ethnicity and is a liberal agnostic Leo. Her Myers-Briggs personality type is ENTJ. Leading an active lifestyle, Alessia enjoys traveling, technology, and fitness. She is a dog-owner who drinks socially but does not smoke or use marijuana or illicit drugs. Alessia doesn't currently have children, but she would like to in the future. Her preferred partner would be a straight man aged 28 to 40, who doesn't smoke or use drugs but who might drink occasionally and partake in exercise sometimes. Like her, her prospective partner must also want children in future.
